>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0 &#8211; April 10, 2020<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-1.PNG?rev=2382641\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-1.PNG?rev=2382641\" alt=\"User Posts Limit Plugin Settings\"><\/a><p>User Posts Limit Plugin Settings<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-2.PNG?rev=2382641\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-2.PNG?rev=2382641\" alt=\"Post creation limit notification\"><\/a><p>Post creation limit notification<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2708415\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2708415\" alt=\"Role option\"><\/a><p>Role option<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2708415\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2708415\" alt=\"Post type option\"><\/a><p>Post type option<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2708415\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/user-posts-limit\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2708415\" alt=\"Users Screen stats\"><\/a><p>Users Screen stats<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Just what I needed to work on a custom post type.<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tacaha5\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/25d5a733b8a4bbf782a95a3c753735e1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/25d5a733b8a4bbf782a95a3c753735e1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tacaha5\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">GinaW <small>(tacaha5)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 5, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin! Lightweight. Does exactly what it should. Thank you!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful plugin!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cheyenneblackmoon\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/313016e8a13297708f96de44552353d0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/313016e8a13297708f96de44552353d0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cheyenneblackmoon\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cheyenneblackmoon<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 2, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin that provides very useful solutions. I have been looking for it for a while.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Possibilities are really interesting for a multisite installation<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ludovicsclain\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ecd98c5fe8fb1cf82eae4d345bc9fbe1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ecd98c5fe8fb1cf82eae4d345bc9fbe1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ludovicsclain\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ludovic S. Clain <small>(ludovicsclain)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 3, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">With a little elbow grease, the possibilities are really interesting for a multisite installation, such as <strong>limiting the total number of WooCommerce products per site<\/strong> (regardless of the author). The plugin is not easy to learn, not very intuitive and would surely deserve to be more explicit on certain settings, however, it does the job and the author is responsive and attentive\u2026 so I recommend it \ud83d\udc4d\u00a0<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">The missing piece in membership sites<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/backpackingseries\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/bc63129c131a06c5498443c7ac5ba3c2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/bc63129c131a06c5498443c7ac5ba3c2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/backpackingseries\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">backpackingseries<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">For the uniqueness it offers, supporting all post-types, a total lack of competition, the simplicity of operation, and that it's 100% free, I wonder why this plugin is not already hitting 100K installs.\n\nAs for features, I would love to see (1) native integrations with membership and subscription plugins, (2) Ability to limit based on parent - child CPT relationships, and (3) better UI\n\nAll said, even in it's current form, this plugin is gold. The author is extremely helpful, willing to login to your site and helping to troubleshoot. It doesn't get better. Truly wish this plugin gets the limelight it deserves. Thank you Condless!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Restrict posts based on user in each role<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gjbyrjyy\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d022a8ca7ad278890a33c20c22a96d29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d022a8ca7ad278890a33c20c22a96d29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gjbyrjyy\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hamed <small>(gjbyrjyy)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 16, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin should be unique in its kind\n\nBut I need something else\nI need an option or code that allows each user in each role to see only their own posts, and completely hide the posts of others, even in search results (without any messages or bookmarks)\n\n**More details:**\nThe user has to log in to get the content, and when he logs in he only sees his posts (as if there are no other posts on the website)\n\nAny help would be appreciated\nThankful<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/saadyfernando\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/aa7b7f7bb69ef6be27b2e4e424938bc6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/aa7b7f7bb69ef6be27b2e4e424938bc6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/saadyfernando\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">saadyfernando<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 17, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It works as you expect it. With excellent customizability. Thanks!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/itsmuxr\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1237a06d4274d024e1bfb6ffe80ac02e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1237a06d4274d024e1bfb6ffe80ac02e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/itsmuxr\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">itsmuxr<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 14, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">A very useful plugin for a WordPress website. I become to use your plugin recently and it really helped us a lot, in order to manage post limits. Thank you and wish you good luck)))<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n