icons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/babylonix\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0b97fd763acb9614503cb325e8104d82?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0b97fd763acb9614503cb325e8104d82?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/babylonix\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">babylonix<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 24, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u0422\u043e \u0447\u0442\u043e \u043d\u0430\u0434\u043e!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
